                {
                  "id": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3s46hs1s/manifest/annotation/p2",
                  "type": "Annotation",
                  "motivation": "commenting",
                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "\n            <p>$8. for the Pentateuch 12 mo; and there are now 3 sets<lb/> 8 vo. left. The three\n                Bibles having been sold, I shall,<lb/> if convenient to you, be willing to receive\n                as many<lb/> more. Perhaps also two or three copies of the Daily<lb/> Prayers in the\n                cheaper bindings would also be<lb/>\n                <sic>saleable</sic>. Have the goodness to send me a copy<lb/> of the first series of\n                your sermons, and also name<lb/> me some others of your publications, for it\n                there<lb/> are among them any which I have not read,<lb/> would like to get one or\n                two. Young <persName>Mr. O.</persName> told me<lb/> some weeks ago that he had got\n                several subscri„<lb/>bers for the work which you are translating, which<lb/> is more\n                than I would have expected. If you can<lb/> find time please answer his letter. I\n                regret to<lb/> notice your observations about the Occident. I<lb/> have not yet seen\n                    <persName>Mr. Myers</persName> since, but from the<lb/> answer which he gave me\n                some months ago, doubt<lb/> that he will be able to get any subscribers.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">My sister left for <placeName>Panama</placeName> shortly after\n                her<lb/> marriage, but I have written your remembrance<lb/> to her. My Father unties\n                with me in best regards.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(3)\">Respy. Yours, <persName role=\"author\">David M. Pizal</persName></p>\n            "
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3s46hs1s/canvas/p2"
                }
